    description: `Hisn ul Muslim (8x12) pocket-size edition is the ultra-compact version of the renowned daily supplication collection compiled by Sa'id bin Ali bin Wahf al-Qahtani, designed to be carried anywhere so that authentic Prophetic du'as are always within reach. This miniature edition packs the complete set of approximately 267 verified supplications into a format small enough to fit in a shirt pocket, wallet, or small bag.\n\nThe 8x12 centimeter dimensions make this the most portable edition of Hisn ul Muslim available. Despite its small size, it retains the complete content of the standard edition, with each du'a presented in Arabic alongside its Urdu translation and hadith source reference. The compact typesetting has been carefully designed to remain legible while maximizing content density. This edition is particularly valuable for people who are frequently on the move — students commuting to school or university, professionals during their workday, travelers, and anyone who wants to maintain the practice of consistent du'a throughout their daily activities.\n\nThe supplications cover the full range of daily needs: waking and sleeping, entering and leaving the home, before and after meals, during travel, at the mosque, in times of difficulty, and for general spiritual wellbeing. The morning and evening adhkar sections provide structured remembrance routines that can be completed in minutes. All du'as have been authenticated through rigorous hadith verification, with the source collection and authentication grade noted for each entry.\n\nThis pocket edition is frequently purchased in multiples — kept in different bags, car glove compartments, office drawers, and bedside tables to ensure constant accessibility. It is a popular choice for distribution during Ramadan, at Islamic conferences, and as a small but meaningful gift. For Urdu-speaking Muslims who understand the importance of making du'a throughout the day but need a reference they can carry everywhere, this pocket-size Hisn ul Muslim provides an indispensable daily companion that keeps the fortress of supplication always at hand.`,
